\DOC PURE_CASE_TAC

\TYPE {tactic}

\SYNOPSIS
Case splits on a term {t} that features in the goal as {case t of ...}

\DESCRIBE
{SingleStep.PURE_CASE_TAC} searches the goal for an instance of
{case t of ...}, and performs a {SingleStep.Cases_on `t`}.

\FAILURE
{SingleStep.PURE_CASE_TAC} fails if there is no instance of
{case t of ...} in the goal, where the {case} term is a case constant in
the typebase and all the free variables of {t} are free in the goal.

\SEEALSO
SingleStep.CASE_TAC.

\ENDDOC
